  * network.py: Added label of network devices in interface dictionary,
    read from /etc/edenwall/hardware/network_devices (e.g. GbE0 for eth0).
  * openvpn.py: Added importCert and importKey services to import
    certificate and key for the server (transmitted as strings).
  * nuconf/: Added a component called Nuconf to serve the definition of
    the menu and the specifications of the pages in the NuConf frontend.

0.2 (2008-07-18)
  * Initial revision for EdenWall 4.
